News.short_description: We will not be uploading highlights from our game against Braintree Town on Boxing Day
News.description:
We would like to apologise to supporters for not being able to upload highlights of Monday's game against Braintree Town.

Unfortunately the footage we received today is not of a suitable quality for us to post on our website, we apologise for any inconvenience caused.

Service will resume from Monday's home Live BT Sport Vanarama National League fixture against Braintree Town.Â
